00:17:11.200 --> 00:17:12.980
we hired at that point there.

00:17:12.980 --> 00:17:17.170
But to do the switch
into IAP, you also

00:17:17.170 --> 00:17:19.790
need people who have
done this before,

00:17:19.790 --> 00:17:24.760
and people with more
expertise, more experience.

00:17:24.760 --> 00:17:27.940
And then London
