00:17:27.940 --> 00:17:30.430
that's very attractive,
that you can actually

00:17:30.430 --> 00:17:33.100
have these people join
you, join the team,

00:17:33.100 --> 00:17:34.430
and then work on this game.

00:17:34.430 --> 00:17:35.770
So that's what we did.

00:17:35.770 --> 00:17:38.710
And launched "Merge Dragons"
from our London office,

00:17:38.710 --> 00:17:40.630
from our London studio.

00:17:40.630 --> 00:17:45.050
And we launched it
