00:23:41.590 --> 00:23:44.130
But in "Merge Dragons,"
you really see

00:23:44.130 --> 00:23:46.290
people who are
fans of that game,

00:23:46.290 --> 00:23:49.540
even more than you are, as
the person who made the game.

00:23:49.540 --> 00:23:50.170
