00:25:56.020 --> 00:26:00.540
I mean, up until August
we did not have any ads

00:26:00.540 --> 00:26:02.300
on "Merge Dragons."

00:26:02.300 --> 00:26:04.400
So it was fully IAP based.

00:26:04.400 --> 00:26:06.380
