00:26:09.870 --> 00:26:13.590
The ads revenues,
there's a bit of,

00:26:13.590 --> 00:26:16.920
I'd say almost a lack of
transparency on the way today

00:26:16.920 --> 00:26:19.480
you get your ad revenues
on a per player basis.

00:26:19.480 --> 00:26:23.220
Like you can't see
how much revenue you

00:26:23.220 --> 00:26:25.390
get for one of your players.

00:26:25.390 --> 00:26:27.720
